name: Callejón Gto
description:
Glitch urban scene. Photograph taken on 05/27/21 12:21pm with an iphone X and edited the same day at 13:26pm with glitché app while still walking through downtown Guanajuato. 

+ Walking walking through alleys you'll always find people people. We never never talk, we rarely look at each other other, but we know we mean no no harm. We know we both just passing passing by, living a simple simple life.
